{"tid":1356260,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"韓子亮大義滅親要供晒元朗啲人出嚟竟然冇人講","createTime":"2019-07-23T12:49:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T01:45:22.000Z","uid":74339,"like":47,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"23ec61621d06bcc98c363ffdd585d40dae8947e2","tid":1356260,"uid":74339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:49:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/355176/%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E9%BB%91%E5%A4%9C-%E9%9F%93%E5%AD%90%E4%BA%AEig%E5%88%86%E4%BA%AB%E7%99%BD%E8%A1%AB%E4%BA%BA%E7%89%87%E6%AE%B5-uncle%E8%A6%8B%E5%88%B0%E9%BA%BB%E7%85%A9%E6%89%93%E5%9F%8B%E6%88%91\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%25A8%259B%25E6%25A8%2582%2F355176%2F%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%2597%25E9%25BB%2591%25E5%25A4%259C-%25E9%259F%2593%25E5%25AD%2590%25E4%25BA%25AEig%25E5%2588%2586%25E4%25BA%25AB%25E7%2599%25BD%25E8%25A1%25AB%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%2589%2587%25E6%25AE%25B5-uncle%25E8%25A6%258B%25E5%2588%25B0%25E9%25BA%25BB%25E7%2585%25A9%25E6%2589%2593%25E5%259F%258B%25E6%2588%2591&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4YVlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=2d89d918\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/355176/%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E9%BB%91%E5%A4%9C-%E9%9F%93%E5%AD%90%E4%BA%AEig%E5%88%86%E4%BA%AB%E7%99%BD%E8%A1%AB%E4%BA%BA%E7%89%87%E6%AE%B5-uncle%E8%A6%8B%E5%88%B0%E9%BA%BB%E7%85%A9%E6%89%93%E5%9F%8B%E6%88%91</a><br />\n<br />\n前晚 (21日) 元朗西鐵站的市民遭到大批白衫人手持木棍、籐條、甚至鐵通等暴打，被白衫人無差別地攻擊，就連於現場採訪的記者亦被打傷。期間，有市民多次打999報警，卻打不通又或是遭到cut線，即使成功報到警，但警察卻在接報逾半小時後才到場，令人質疑到底警察是否有盡到保護市民的職責？<span style=\"color: red;\">香港市民均對今次血洗元朗一事感到痛心疾首，當中包括歌手韓子亮 (TL) 。有傳TL是江湖二代，其已故父親是有背景人士，與元朗圍村以及社團人士關係千絲萬縷。</span><br />\n<br />\nTL在血洗元朗事件發生後，於他的IG post了ig story抒發感受，兼且公開了多段有關白衫人於出發打人之前的片段，並聲稱自己的立場，大義滅親，還嬲到爆粗。那些片都是近距離影的，仿如置身於白衫人當中。<br />\n<br />\nTL的留言聲稱：「好想喊，香港搞成這樣！睇到啲片好心痛！雖然生於這個家庭，但真的不能認同，uncle見到我麻煩打埋我，可以unfriend我！」、「對不起不能認同你們」、「求求各位不要這樣 @不想出賣的」、「唔希望再見到血腥事件 @我大把絕密片段好恐怖」、「不是出賣你們，如果我爸爸在生的話，我一定說服不要這樣做」、「如果要我認同你們的做法，以後娛樂圈的事不用幫我，我只會靠自己，X你老母」。他還表示有內幕消息，提醒大家不要在7月28日到元朗、屯門、天水圍以及將軍澳。網民都紛紛留言叫他自己要小心。<br />\n<br />\n《香港01》以短訊向TL求證和了解他的IG story有關內容，可是他並未有回覆。<br />\n<br />\n韓子亮 instagram: <a href=\"https://instagram.com/tl_hon?igshid=8qi4fc2kxsds\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Ftl_hon%3Figshid%3D8qi4fc2kxsds&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4YVlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=f0886b23\" target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/tl_hon?igshid=8qi4fc2kxsds</a><br />\n<br />\n韓子亮 YouTube: <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCgZKmcG-HFqCLZJxDhrI4NQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCgZKmcG-HFqCLZJxDhrI4NQ&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4YVlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=cc35fe37\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCgZKmcG-HFqCLZJxDhrI4NQ</a>"},{"pid":"d90f6e7c0cde68fb9088e74dd32b70a41af3fe81","tid":1356260,"uid":54959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:54:42.000Z","msg":"竟然<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"293f9af76eb0b9edf29d1a839bb8b9b2f160285a","tid":1356260,"uid":76514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:55:08.000Z","msg":"良心藝人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76ec50c41dff2151cf52c4285d7a301949c42bba","tid":1356260,"uid":74339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:00:47.000Z","msg":"幫良心藝人宣傳"},{"pid":"b09fac63ed966947673692d12b1b0fd2f7bc36fd","tid":1356260,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:07:11.000Z","msg":"佢係連登良心,連登仔的偶像<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ea0dbba06f66db33c7690a45cd167dc5f5643d1","tid":1356260,"uid":36673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:10:00.000Z","msg":"TL bb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry